   <body>
      <context>You can respond to a comment posted by any user. The date the response is posted is also saved.</context>
      <ol>
         <li href="../../../Warehouse/Task_Warehouse/AcsPrjContDocsNav.dita#task-5739/AccProContDocFolder">
            <p/>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select a document, and then click <uicontrol>Comment Log</uicontrol>. </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>COMMENT LOG</uicontrol> page is displayed.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select a comment, and then click <uicontrol>Edit </uicontrol> to respond to the comment. </p>
            <p>The <uicontrol>Responded By</uicontrol> column is updated with the user name of the logged-in user. 
                    <p>The <uicontrol>Responded On</uicontrol> column displays the response received date.</p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>In the selected row, double-click in the <uicontrol>Response</uicontrol> column, and enter a response to the comment.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the <uicontrol>Complete</uicontrol> check box if the comment has received an appropriate response.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>. </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
